<h3>About the Institute:</h3>
<div style="background-color:ffff66;">
<p>
Bhubaneswar Institute of technology is among the premier institutes of India.
It is the no. 1 engineering college in East India. Started just as a school in 
1997 with just 12 students , it has come a long way since then, and today 25 
years later , we can proudly say that creating this institute under the tutelage
of <u><b>Shri. Bhuvan Goswami</b></u> was one of the best decisions ever taken for the education 
of children in East India.
</p>
<p>
This university not only provides quality education but also an environment which 
is essential for mental peace of the student. The entire campus is surrouded by 
lush green fields, which is a treat to the eyes.
</p>
